# --- Go build artifacts ---
# Compiled binaries (project name + any one-off main packages)
/clinics
/api
/server
/cmd/*/clinics
/cmd/*/api

# Standard Go output / object files
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
*.out

# Coverage / profiling
*.coverprofile
coverage.txt
coverage.html
*.prof

# Vendored deps (we use modules; vendor/ should never be committed here)
/vendor/

# --- Environment & secrets ---
# We read ../laravel-doc/.env, but anyone may stage a local override
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Editor / IDE ---
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- macOS / OS noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Logs & local state ---
*.log
/tmp/
/.cache/

# --- Generated artifacts ---
# Generated OpenAPI server code (Step 3 will configure oapi-codegen).
# Keep this commented out — typically the generated file IS committed so
# CI/builds don't depend on local code-gen. Uncomment if you decide to
# regenerate on every build instead.
# /internal/api/openapi.gen.go
